-street-view.jpeg/96x54-cropped/a-history-of-the-world-according-to-getty-images-2022-vintage-street-view.jpeg" imageAltText="" standfirst="Our annual poll spotlights 181 unique video essays, nominated by 48 international voters, showcasing the breadth and depth of current videographic practice." class="ArticleCard__Outer-sc-zrtbni-0 eIZIIS articleCard polls"><div class="ArticleCard__CategoryTag-sc-zrtbni-7 yMPPW">polls</div><div class="ArticleCard__PageImageContainer-sc-zrtbni-5 ehvIXQ"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImage-sc-zrtbni-6 hiiFMo image"></div></div><h3 class="ArticleCard__Heading-sc-zrtbni-3 bynrVe">The best video essays of 2023</h3><div class="ArticleCard__Meta-sc-zrtbni-1 edgoES"><p class="ArticleCard__Author-sc-zrtbni-2 KIAzD">By Queline Meadows</p></div><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/polls/best-video-essays-2023" title="Read The best video essays of 2023" class="ArticleCard__CallToAction-sc-zrtbni-4 fwpHHm"><span>The best video essays of 2023</span></a></article><article image48x27="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2023-12/killers-of-the-flower-moon-2023-osage-women-being-photographed.jpg/96x54-cropped/killers-of-the-flower-moon-2023-osage-women-being-photographed.jpg" imageAltText="" standfirst="We asked 106 contributors  British and international  to pick the top ten movies they&#x27;d seen in 2023. You can browse all 363 choices they nominated here." class="ArticleCard__Outer-sc-zrtbni-0 eIZIIS articleCard polls"><div class="ArticleCard__CategoryTag-sc-zrtbni-7 yMPPW">polls</div><div class="ArticleCard__PageImageContainer-sc-zrtbni-5 ehvIXQ"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImage-sc-zrtbni-6 fTkbdQ image"></div></div><h3 class="ArticleCard__Heading-sc-zrtbni-3 bynrVe">The best films of 2023  all the votes</h3><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-and-sound/polls/best-films-2023-all-votes" title="Read The best films of 2023  all the votes" class="ArticleCard__CallToAction-sc-zrtbni-4 fwpHHm"><span>The best films 